# Web3Forms — required for /contact form submissions.
# The NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix exposes this to the browser (required — the form
# POSTs directly from the client to Web3Forms). Lock the key to specific
# domains in the Web3Forms dashboard so exposure is harmless.
#
# 1. Sign in at https://web3forms.com/
# 2. Create an access key associated with jonathanlai928@gmail.com
# 3. In the key's settings, restrict Allowed Domains to:
#      johnnybuildstech.com, *.vercel.app
# 4. Paste the UUID here AND in Vercel project env vars.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
